      "        - description: Repeat title [instead: remove | offer description]",
      "        - description: Rephrase title [instead: remove | offer description]",
      "*/}",
      "",
      "{/* ==========================PAGE TAXONOMY GUIDE========================= */}",
      "{/*",
      "DO:",
      "- Use Colored Badges or icons to provide major category differentiation",
